DESCRIPTION:Celebrate the holiday with a refined prix-fixe brunch at **Lott
	e Hotel Seattle’s**\, **Charlotte Restaurant & Lounge**\, featuring elevat
	ed dishes like Dungeness crab tartlet\, ube pancakes and lamb benedict\, a
	ccompanied by live jazz from Second Dimension. Guests can enjoy stunning v
	iews of Elliott Bay in a luxurious\, family-friendly setting. Reservations
	 are recommended.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/celebra
	te-easter-at-lotte-hotel-seattle/18379819/2026-04-05T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday -
